{"tid":2080342,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇絲打既男朋友係想結婚 但自己反而唔太知自己想點","createTime":"2020-06-26T10:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T14:28:52.000Z","uid":61288,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ae9d696dc7bc3772f5ad9e1715ce6f9787d29e85","tid":2080342,"uid":61288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T10:54:54.000Z","msg":"幾日前同男友睇完金都後，開始反思緊自己想要咩<br />\n同男朋友一齊左差唔多一年，但佢就成日會講結婚呢樣野<br />\n佢由同我第一日一齊已經講明係會以結婚為前題而同我一齊，所以佢好似成日都好想結婚咁。<br />\n<br />\n睇緊金都時，有一幕係講有對新人影結婚相，對新人要擺pose，我男朋友突然間同我講，如果我地第時結婚，我地都要咁做<br />\n<br />\n其實唔知佢係咪真係知結婚係咩一回事，定係佢為結而結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇人另一半係咁"},{"pid":"5e875aae270595acff06d86e058aab74a28e43c3","tid":2080342,"uid":17492,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T10:55:44.000Z","msg":"一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53cc1cd8a0373009ebca3230e2b45bb911e61ccc","tid":2080342,"uid":203889,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T10:56:52.000Z","msg":"我諗你唔駛太認真<br />\nhea應咪算羅<br />\n佢應該都係隨口up下"},{"pid":"dfceac9bdaa5f10401711c6f1667269bd5b6ef51","tid":2080342,"uid":311573,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T10:57:20.000Z","msg":"樓主幾歲<br />\n樓主男友幾歲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50bd5eb800420e5e2dd8e2347370958755629d2","tid":2080342,"uid":155818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T10:57:52.000Z","msg":"你男友屎忽痕心upup姐無事既"},{"pid":"2fc8e469f0e1fc0596d75bcdc29124c0e73d478b","tid":2080342,"uid":203889,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T10:58:43.000Z","msg":"下年仲係咪一齊緊都好難講<br />\n（唔係咒你，只係一日未有實際行動（儲錢，book野&hellip;）都唔好信）"},{"pid":"97fb951f29845c34